      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in truly mint condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards, preserving its showroom-floor integrity both aesthetically and mechanically. With an unblemished history and exhaustive service records, it represents the pinnacle of its class. We invite the most discerning collectors to experience a vehicle that defies its age, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
