      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that distinguishes it from the typical secondary market offering. This specimen exhibits pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity, reflecting a history of fastidious stewardship and climate-controlled storage. For the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in showroom-equivalent condition. Serious inquiries only.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
